\f0\fs20 \cf0 Codes also distinguish between personal and corporate distress. Both may impact firm-creation. For example, in the U.S. a fifth of personal bankruptcy filings fall under small business debt [#Sullivan1999] and states with debtor-friendlier terms in personal bankruptcy have higher rates of small-business ownership amongst comparable groups [#Fan2003]. This dissertation focuses, however, on corporate bankruptcy which likely has the greater effect.}

